---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../site.config";

const updatedAt = siteConfig.updatedAt;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="免责声明与版权声明 | 异环攻略站"
  description="异环攻略站免责声明与版权声明，说明本站为玩家自建同人攻略站，相关游戏素材版权归属完美世界/Hotta Studio，攻略数据不保证绝对实时准确。"
  jsonLd={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    name: "免责声明与版权声明",
    dateModified: updatedAt
  }}
>
  <article class="prose lang-zh max-w-none">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neon">Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>免责声明与版权声明</h1>
    <p>最后更新日期：{updatedAt}</p>

    <div class="my-8 rounded-lg border border-amber/40 bg-amber/10 p-5">
      <p class="font-bold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">重要声明</p>
      <p>
        本站为玩家自建攻略站，与《异环》（Neverness to Everness / NTE）官方、Hotta Studio、完美世界及其关联公司没有商业合作、官方授权、代理或从属关系。站内出现的游戏名称、Logo、角色、截图、宣传图、视频封面等素材版权和商标权归原权利人所有，本站仅用于攻略说明、评论、资料索引和玩家交流。
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. 非官方网站说明</h2>
    <p>
      《异环攻略站 | Neverness to Everness 中文指南》（以下简称“本站”）为玩家自建的同人攻略与资料整理网站，主要用于分享《异环》（Neverness to Everness / NTE）的角色培养、机制解析、地图探索、工具计算和版本资讯等内容。
    </p>
    <p>
      本站并非《异环》官方网站，也不代表游戏开发商、发行商或其关联公司的官方立场。本站与完美世界、Hotta Studio 及其相关品牌之间不存在官方合作、授权代理或从属关系，除非页面中另有明确说明。
    </p>

    <h2>2. 版权归属</h2>
    <p>
      《异环》游戏名称、标识、角色、世界观设定、游戏截图、宣传图、视频、音乐、文本、角色素材及其他相关知识产权，版权和商标权归属于其合法权利人，包括但不限于完美世界、Hotta Studio 及相关版权方。
    </p>
    <p>
      本站可能在攻略说明、资料整理或内容引用中使用部分游戏图片、角色素材、文本描述或公开宣传资料，仅用于非商业性的攻略展示、评论、介绍与玩家交流目的。相关素材的版权仍归原权利人所有。
    </p>
    <p>
      除本站原创排版、攻略文字、工具说明和站点结构外，任何来自游戏官方、商店页面、公开宣传资料或游戏截图的素材均不视为本站原创资产。未经原权利人授权，本站不会将相关素材单独打包售卖、授权转售或声称拥有其版权。
    </p>

    <h2>3. 数据准确性声明</h2>
    <p>
      本站会尽力根据公开资料、测试体验、玩家反馈和版本更新维护攻略内容，但不对游戏数据的绝对实时性、完整性或准确性作出担保。
    </p>
    <p>
      由于游戏仍可能处于测试、更新或平衡调整阶段，角色数值、技能效果、材料需求、抽卡规则、地图点位和机制描述可能随版本变化而失效。请以游戏内实际内容、官方公告和最新版本为准。
    </p>

    <h2>4. 使用风险</h2>
    <p>
      本站提供的攻略、配队建议、抽卡计算和养成规划仅供参考，不构成任何强制性建议。用户因参考本站内容产生的游戏资源消耗、账号决策或其他结果，由用户自行判断和承担。
    </p>

    <h2>5. 侵权处理</h2>
    <p>
      如果你是相关权利人，认为本站内容存在版权、商标或其他权益问题，请通过 <a href="/contact/">联系我们</a> 页面与我们联系，并提供可验证的权利证明和具体页面链接。我们将在核实后及时处理，包括修改、标注来源或删除相关内容。
    </p>
    <p>
      权利人联系时建议提供：权利主体名称、授权或权属证明、涉及页面 URL、存在争议的具体图片或文字、希望采取的处理方式。本站会优先处理清晰、可核验的版权或商标反馈。
    </p>

    <h2>6. 广告与商业独立性</h2>
    <p>
      本站可能通过 Google AdSense 等广告服务展示广告，用于分担服务器、域名和内容维护成本。广告展示不代表游戏官方认可本站内容，也不代表本站与广告主、游戏开发商或发行商存在合作关系。
    </p>

    <h2>7. 声明更新</h2>
    <p>
      本站可能根据内容维护、版权要求或法律法规变化调整本声明。更新后会在本页面修改“最后更新日期”。
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="prose lang-en max-w-none">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neon">Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer and Copyright Notice</h1>
    <p>Last updated: {updatedAt}</p>

    <div class="my-8 rounded-lg border border-amber/40 bg-amber/10 p-5">
      <p class="font-bold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">Important Notice</p>
      <p>
        This is a fan-made guide site. It has no official partnership, authorization, agency relationship or affiliation with Neverness to Everness, Hotta Studio, Perfect World or related companies. Game names, logos, characters, screenshots, promotional images and similar materials belong to their respective rights holders and are used only for guide commentary, reference and player information.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Unofficial Fan Site Notice</h2>
    <p>
      NTE Guide is an unofficial fan-made guide and reference site for Neverness to Everness. It shares character building, system explanations, map exploration, calculator tools and version notes.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is not the official Neverness to Everness website and does not represent the developer, publisher or their affiliates unless a specific page states otherwise.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Copyright Ownership</h2>
    <p>
      The Neverness to Everness name, marks, characters, world setting, screenshots, promotional images, videos, music, text and related intellectual property belong to their lawful owners, including but not limited to Perfect World, Hotta Studio and related rights holders.
    </p>
    <p>
      Game assets may appear in guides for non-commercial commentary, reference, explanation and player discussion. Those assets remain the property of their rights holders. The site does not sell, sublicense or claim ownership over official game materials.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Accuracy Notice</h2>
    <p>
      We try to maintain guides using public information, testing experience, player feedback and version updates, but we do not guarantee that all game data is always complete, current or error-free.
    </p>
    <p>
      Character values, skills, material requirements, pull rules, map locations and mechanics may change by version. In-game information and official announcements should be treated as the final source.
    </p>

    <h2>4. User Decision Risk</h2>
    <p>
      Guides, team suggestions, pull calculations and growth plans are references only. Players are responsible for their own resource use and account decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Copyright Handling</h2>
    <p>
      If you are a rights holder and believe content on this site creates a copyright, trademark or attribution issue, contact us with the page URL, disputed material and verifiable rights documentation. After review, we may revise, add attribution or remove the relevant material.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Advertising and Commercial Independence</h2>
    <p>
      This site may display ads through Google AdSense or similar services to help cover hosting, domain and content maintenance costs. Ads do not mean the game publisher endorses this site, and advertising does not control guide conclusions.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Updates</h2>
    <p>
      This disclaimer may be updated as site content, rights requests or legal requirements change. The last updated date will be revised when the page changes.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
